<span id="freeTextContainer1679938983289694465">It wasn&apos;t until the very end of this book that I realised exactly how much I loved it. I am unsure if I would call it enjoyable, more like a very well written, intelligent and absorbing read rather than something I would call uplifting. It&apos;s definitely haunting, and definitely something everyone should read.</span>
  <span id="freeText1679938983289694465" style="display:none">It wasn't until the very end of this book that I realised exactly how much I loved it. I am unsure if I would call it enjoyable, more like a very well written, intelligent and absorbing read rather than something I would call uplifting. It's definitely haunting, and definitely something everyone should read.</span>
